Package: ggvariant
Title: Tidy, ggplot2-Native Visualization for Genomic Variants
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Your", "AYO JOASH JOSHUA", email = "joashjoshua789@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: A simple, opinionated toolkit for visualizing genomic variant data
    using a ggplot2-native grammar. Accepts VCF files or plain data frames and
    produces publication-ready lollipop plots, consequence summaries, mutational
    spectrum charts, and cohort-level comparisons with minimal code. Designed for
    both wet-lab biologists and experienced bioinformaticians.
